snippet.title: A Change of Heart [Trailer]
snippet.description:
A Change of Heart: A Magical Girl Adventure. Now released for free to play in-browser!
https://shibeyfacegames.itch.io/a-change-of-heart-a-magical-girl-adventure


Entry to the April 2020 Magical Girl Game Jam on itch.io. Made in just over two weeks by ShibeyFaceGames. Original soundtrack and sound design by Facemelting Solos.


ShibeyFaceGames: https://shibeyfacegames.itch.io/
Twitter: http://twitter.com/ShibeyG


Facemelting Solos: https://facemeltingsolos.itch.io/
Twitter: http://twitter.com/Facemeltingsolo
